<DOC><DOCNO> DOE2-64-1189 </DOCNO><TEXT>The benefit of implementing advanced control strategies in electricalrenewable energy systems (RES) has been investigated systematically.Under consideration are strategies using: forecasts of the meteorologicalvariables that determine the renewable energy production, and climaticinformation obtained from meteorological time series. The required systemstructures of RES, in order to yield a benefit from these strategies,are discussed in particular. 6 figs.</TEXT></DOC>